title: IAA Tonight | Lamar Gives the Ravens a Deadline for a New Deal
description: Lamar Jackson has officially given the Ravens until Friday to agree to a new deal or contract talks won't be further discussed until after the season. Why can't the Ravens and Lamar find the correct number that will make both sides happy? Plus, Brandon Marshall, Leger Douzable, and Omar Kelly play Fact or Cap: NFL Opening Weekend Edition.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Omar KElly, Brandon Marshall, Leger Douzable)
